with what's there so what's the first thing they did as soon as the announcement was made y'all remember a couple weeks ago they tore it all down construction sometimes starts with the demolishing what doesn't work and getting a firm foundation and new foundation for something that's going to be there and construction in our words needs to with grace help and heal and guide not

