15:15.736 --> 15:25.170
There's something about loving others that we sometimes miss, especially when we have good intent, but the wrong way to go about doing it.

15:25.691 --> 15:27.954
Because sometimes we're all focused on the truth,

15:28.226 --> 15:34.115
or we're focused on love and not both, but truth without love actually wounds someone.

15:35.197 --> 15:38.862
