15:40.925 --> 15:46.213
In Ephesians 4 verse 15 it says, we need to speak the truth in love.

15:47.395 --> 15:48.376
Truth and love.

15:48.437 --> 15:54.085
We talked about it in previous sermon a little bit about that, but I want to go a little further with it.

15:54.125 --> 15:57.330
The truth without love becomes harshness.

15:58.722 --> 16:01.406
