16:04.351 --> 16:06.795
You don't want harshness and you don't want compromise.

16:08.457 --> 16:11.742
A safe church does not celebrate sin.

16:12.484 --> 16:13.105
It doesn't.

16:13.605 --> 16:17.391
And it refuses to also crush sinners.

16:19.274 --> 16:21.117
So we're not saying, oh, it's okay.

16:21.698 --> 16:22.560
You go ahead and sin.

16:22.600 --> 16:24.302
God's got bigger grace in your sin.

16:24.342 --> 16:26.706
And we don't go the other extreme and go,

16:26.786 --> 16:27.848
You got to stop doing that.

16:27.888 --> 16:32.515
