16:54.242 --> 16:59.188
And so those kind of statements you've maybe seen, I can't believe they're here.

17:00.970 --> 17:06.117
The only person needs to say that is a person walking through that I can't believe I'm here and that ceiling didn't fall down type thing.

17:06.998 --> 17:08.960
They're the only persons I can't believe I'm here.

17:09.922 --> 17:11.463
Not someone else can't believe they're here.

17:13.927 --> 17:14.687
What are they doing here?

17:15.829 --> 17:19.954
