18:50.972 --> 18:51.813
And I don't like it.

18:53.054 --> 18:58.842
And maybe I'm not thinking clearly, but I don't like it.

18:59.143 --> 19:00.405
That were my words were.

19:00.645 --> 19:02.407
That was my words.

19:02.487 --> 19:06.413
I had written down at work that day about that situation.

19:06.433 --> 19:08.796
I don't remember though my heart ain't that funny.

