20:10.594 --> 20:17.242
So I got truth from dad and love from mom, and I'm thinking, why can't they both get together on this thing?

20:17.282 --> 20:22.728
And I get some of both and, but my mom would always go, it's all right, son, it'll be okay.

20:24.290 --> 20:27.834
I could be doing some of the stupidest things in the world, making her upset.

20:29.055 --> 20:34.161
This is probably a nightmare situation for a church, but at the time I didn't think about it.

20:34.742 --> 20:38.706
I accidentally peeled a small piece, we're in the parsley now.

20:38.914 --> 20:40.677
in my bedroom of the wallpaper.

