And I accidentally bumped the wall and I saw under it a nice pretty coral color.

20:52.715 --> 20:59.726
So I proceeded to pull off the wallpaper off the wall that they had paper before we moved in.

20:59.786 --> 21:03.772
And my mother looks and there's strips of wallpaper still on hanging.

