29:39.471 --> 29:45.318
The one thing we first do is we look for ways to share our hope with others, to know what it is.

29:46.980 --> 29:52.946
And when you hear somebody gossip about somebody say, let's not talk about them, let's talk to them so we can do to help.

29:55.669 --> 29:57.131
That would be an interesting thing.

29:57.391 --> 29:58.472
You see what she's wearing over here?

29:58.773 --> 30:03.538
