30:04.418 --> 30:09.703
that we can come alongside her and help her so that she doesn't feel embarrassed.

30:10.664 --> 30:12.746
You know, that's where you change gossip and to grace.

30:14.908 --> 30:24.277
And if we forgive quickly, we need to set the example and show the example that we've set by offering it to the person in a way that's real.

